parameters.name: BR
parameters.description:
RTN radial component of the magnetic-field in nT.                       
      The radial component (R) points from the Sun to the spacecraft,         
      positive away from the Sun.

parameters.name: BT
parameters.description:
RTN tangential component of the magnetic-field in nT.                   
      The tangential component (T) is parallel to the Solar Equatorial        
      plane (Omega Sun x R).

parameters.name: BN
parameters.description:
RTN normal component of the magnetic-field in nT.                       
      The normal component (N) completes the right handed set, and            
      is roughly normal to the Solar Equatorial plane (R x Phi).

parameters.name: BTOTAL
parameters.description:
Average value of the full-resolution magnetic-field magnitudes          
      calculated over the averaging interval in nT. Note that this value      
      may differ slightly from the square root of the sum of the squares      
      of the averaged field components.

parameters.name: NPTS
parameters.description: Number of points in the average.
